Class TransitionMap<S extends Enum<S>>

java.lang.Object
common.core.fsm.TransitionMap<S>
Type Parameters:
S - The enum type that represents the states of the graph
public class TransitionMap<S extends Enum<S>> extends Object
A graph that represents transitions between states of an enum.
